    "## **2.0 ASK PHASE:**\n",
    "\n",
    "This project addresses a business question, a strategic one in fact, and as such has the interest of Bellabeat’s top decision-makers. The following are the stakeholders on this project.\n",
    "•\tUrška Sršen - Bellabeat cofounder and Chief Creative Officer\n",
    "•\tSando Mur - Bellabeat cofounder and a key member of Bellabeat’s executive team\n",
    "•\tBellabeat Marketing Analytics team\n",
    "\n",
    "**What they really want to do.**\n",
    "\n",
    "Bellabeat wanted to reduce uncertainty in the business’s decisions on their marketing strategies, by knowing:\n",
    "\n",
    "    What Interests potential users, what did they want to know and track about their health?\n",
    "    What features were potential users most likely to need and use?\n",
    "    What and how can the Bellabeat product sell to potential users as it benefits?\n",
    "\n",
    "**What I have helped them with.**\n",
    "\n",
    "I have analysed a publicly available dataset of 31 users who consented to the submission of their personal FitBit tracker data, about things like physical activity and sleep monitoring to:\n",
    "\n",
    "    Understand how potential users will use their smart devices from some of the trends in smart device usage from the study\n",
    "    Use the analysis to help Bellabeat make marketing strategy decisions.\n",
    "\n"
   ]
  },
